snippet.title: Pellet Dodge BETA Gameplay Showcase Trailer | v0.8.9.1+
snippet.description:
I still make games, here's the updated trailer. It's grown a lot so please check it out on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2474790/Pellet_Dodge/

OR at: https://mysticaldevelopers.itch.io/pellet-dodge-remastered

Thank you so much for watching and reading and please take the time to check out the project I've spent almost 2 years on.
